   <talk_paragraph index="n193_santaund-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n193_santaund-1-a" mid="16" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You know how urgent the problem is. I'm asking the Hound for help.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$SantaHound$<BR>He has forced us to do overtime work and even work through the night. But now he is asking me for help because he's in trouble, bowwow.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n193_santaund-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n193_santaund-1-b" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>If you perform can one miracle, then you can get out of the roof.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$SantaHound$<BR>Grrrrr, do you think of me as just an ordinary Hound?<BR>Although I'm able to do nothing stuck in the roof, I can perform lots of miracles for Hounds.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n193_santaund-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n193_santaund-1-c" mid="20" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(SantaHound's pride is hurt, his ears are down.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>$SantaHound$<BR>Tha...that's...mmm.<BR>I took SantaHound's course as quickly as possible, couldn't practice the miracle of getting out of the roof.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n193_santaund-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n193_santaund-1-d" mid="22" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(SantaHound is thinking.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$SantaHound$<BR>I can't help crying if I think that Hounds are in pain at this moment while I'm stuck here. Poor Hounds are working without weekends in the forge over here.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n193_santaund-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n193_santaund-1-e" mid="24" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>So, sorry. I'm also forced by circumstances......</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$SantaHound$<BR>Are you forcing me to sign to prove lies like this?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n193_santaund-1-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n193_santaund-1-f" mid="26" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(SantaHound seems to hit upon something.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$SantaHound$<BR>Shut up! I don't want to hear excuses.<BR>Hmm, there might be a way though.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n193_santaund-1-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n193_santaund-3" mid="29" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Accept)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n193_santaund-1-g" mid="30" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Reject)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$SantaHound$<BR>I have a suggestion you can never reject.<BR>I'll sign it if you want me to, but you should become an angel of Hound giving dreams and hopes to Hounds on my behalf.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n193_santaund-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n193_santaund-2" mid="33" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$SantaHound$<BR>I suggested a good way, but you rejected it.<BR>Come again when you change your mind.<BR>If my mind hasn't changed by then, who knows, I might sign.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n193_santaund-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n193_santaund-3" mid="35" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Accept)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n193_santaund-2-a" mid="38" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Reject)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$SantaHound$<BR>What are you thinking?<BR>Did you change your mind to be the angel of Hound?<BR>Then I can sign on it.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n193_santaund-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>$SantaHound$<BR>I can change my mind whenever I want so don't regret it later.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n193_santaund-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n193_santaund-3-a" mid="42" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Show SantaHound the paper to sign.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="41"><![CDATA[<html>$SantaHound$<BR>Okay, then I'll sign it.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n193_santaund-3-a" image="QM_Hound_ice.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n193_santaund-4" mid="44" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Thank you.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="43"><![CDATA[<html>$SantaHound$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(SantaHound puts up his forepaw and leaves his footprint on the paper)</FONT><BR>Anyway I signed.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n193_santaund-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$SantaHound$<BR>Don't forget the promise.<BR>If you break the promise, you'll have a nightmare of being chased by Hounds every night.<BR>However, if you keep the promise well, I'll bless you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-5" mid="49" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Yes, and I got his signature.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="48"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Was there a talking Hound really?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-5" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-5-a" mid="77" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You are convinced just by seeing the footprint. Great.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="76"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Footprint of chimney ash! It is definitely the talking Hound's signature.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-5-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-5-b" mid="79" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Not at all.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="78"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>I've been living with Hounds at the forge for decades. I can figure out a Hound's history just by the Hound's footprint. Good job, young man!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
